high_descs: Turn to the green counter on your left.
Pick up the silver knife in front of the martini glass.
Put the knife in the martini glass.
Pick up the glass containing the knife.
Turn and go to the sink behind you.
Set the glass, with the knife in it, into the sink, near the front edge, to the right of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Move a knife in a martini glass to the sink.

high_descs: Go to the table on the left.
Pick up the silver knife on the table.
Put the knife in the glass on the right, in front of the bottle.
Pick up the glass with the knife from the table.
Turn around, bring the glass with knife to the sink.
Put the glass with knife in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with knife in the sink.

high_descs: Head left to the kitchen table
Put the butter knife in the wine glass
Take the wine glass from the table
Put the glass in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the butter knife in the wine glass, put the glass in the sink
